---
// Skip Link Component - First element in <body> on every page
---

<a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Skip to main content</a>

<style>
  .skip-link {
    position: absolute;
    top: -40px;
    left: 6px;
    background: #000;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    border-radius: 0 0 4px 4px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    transition: top 0.2s ease-in-out;
  }

  .skip-link:focus {
    top: 0;
    outline: 2px solid #005fcc;
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .skip-link:hover:focus {
    background: #333;
  }
</style>